      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "METALHEAD (2) finished out of the money when fresh from a spell two starts back then he was always well out of his ground and was beaten 6 lengths when fourth in a 1207m contest at this track three weeks ago. Best figures measure up nicely. Sure to run well. SKIMBLE SHANKS (4) has switched yards since finishing third five weeks ago over 1710m at this track. Rates highly so expect him to be prominent. TOWN'S WARRIOR (5) was disappointing over 1207m at this track (Dirt) last time out when in the market. That followed a good second the run prior. Has started three times at this course and distance and is yet to miss the placings. Likely improver with strong prospects. COMMINGLING (1) was beaten 8 lengths into sixth in a 1207m contest at this track at his latest appearance. Suitably placed so can turn things around. Something for the Multiples: WHAT DOES IT TAKE (6)",
